                     go to stp-srt-inp-oct-235.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Test su status riga di addebito *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        d-qev-roc-sts-rda    not  = 02
                     go to stp-srt-inp-oct-200.
           go to     stp-srt-inp-oct-240.
       stp-srt-inp-oct-235.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se quantita' in corso di spedizione *
      *                          * a zero : riciclo                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        d-qev-roc-qta-ics    =    zero
                     go to stp-srt-inp-oct-200.
           go to     stp-srt-inp-oct-240.
       stp-srt-inp-oct-236.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se solo ordini gia' evasi               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se riga di addebito                 *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-srt-inp-wtp    not  = "A"
                     go to stp-srt-inp-oct-237.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
