      *                  * record letto                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-sel-bir-ocr-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-liv-det-bir-200.
       prn-liv-det-bir-410.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se estremi evasione gia' trattati      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       prn-liv-det-bir-600.
