       prn-liv-det-bir-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-bir-200.
       prn-liv-det-bir-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-bir-999.
       prn-liv-det-bir-999.
